c Health</span>. 2009; 9: 56. </span></div><div><span class="fm-vol-iss-date">Published online 2009 Feb 12. </span>  <span class="doi">doi:\xc2\xa0<a href="//dx.doi.org/10.1186%2F1471-2458-9-56" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=2654560&amp;issue-id=354737&amp;journal-id=3814&amp;FROM=Article%7CFront%20Matter&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CCrosslink%7CDOI">10.1186/1471-2458-9-56</a></span></div></div></div><div class="inline_block four_col va_top show-overflow align_right"><div class="fm-citation-ids"><div class="fm-citation-pmcid"><span class="fm-citation-ids-label">PMCID: </span><span>PMC2654560</span></div><div class="fm-citation-pmid">PMID: <a href="/pubmed/19216738">19216738</a></div></div></div></div><h1 class="content-title">Healthcare workers\' attitudes to working during pandemic influenza: a qualitative study</h1><div class="half_rhythm"><div class="contrib-group fm-author"><a href="/pubmed/?term=Ives%20J%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=19216738" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm140264434923776" co-class="co-affbox">Jonathan Ives</a>,<sup>1</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Greenfield%20S%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=19216738" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm140264438326576" co-class="co-affbox">Sheila Greenfield</a>,<sup>2</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Parry%20JM%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=19216738" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm140264434920768" co-class="co-affbox">Jayne M Parry</a>,<sup>3</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Draper%20H%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=19216738" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm140264442549248" co-class="co-affbox">Heather Draper</a>,<sup><img src="/corehtml/pmc/pmcgifs/corrauth.gif" alt="corresponding author" /></sup><sup>1</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Gratus%20C%5BAuthor%5D&amp;cauthor=true&amp;cauthor_uid=19216738" class="affpopup" co-rid="_co_idm140264447753360" co-class="co-affbox">Christine Gratus</a>,<sup>2</sup> <a href="/pubmed/?term=Petts%20JI%5BAuthor%